title: Jacobs' Orchestra Monthly
aka: Jacobs' Orchestra Monthly and The Cadenza
additional-notes: Absorbed The Cadenza in April 1924, and for a few years afterwards published under the title 'Jacobs' Orchestra Monthly and the Cadenza' before reverting to its original name.
This periodical includes sheet music that might have renewals under Music, rather than under Contributions to Periodicals. We have not systematically surveyed Music copyright renewals.
